reviews.text: the fish was raw. after we had asked them to cook the fish, the fish was still raw and watery. whats worse, the staffs are rude and arrogant, saying that they will call the police if we kept agruing with them. never in my life have i feel so unsatisfied in a restaurant. the restaurant should be reported by more people. this is intolerable
Food was good and most of the dishes came rapidly. However, it took forever for a dish outside of the set menu. We had asked the staff to follow up twice and it never came.

The first time having dinner in this restaurant and I ordered a dinner sets with chicken rice, fried morning glory, non-spicy minced pork soup and a assorted dish of appetizers. Unexpectedly the appetizers were all quite good, yet the chicken rice and minced pork soup was just so-so. The dinner sets provided with drinks too and when u paid less than hkd300 for two, for dinner, it's still acceptable.
HKD70 pp. Food tastes good with generous portion. The best part is the place is not packed like some other place.
Ray in bog.

reviews.text: 年多前來留下美好印象，今次套餐組合多樣化，不過不失
下午茶唔錯。地方舒適
佢哋嘅海南雞飯套餐一流，雞肉嫩滑，油飯好香，醬汁同羗蓉好好味，仲有一碗椰子雞湯; 炒雜菜好夠火喉。👍
好多套餐選擇。環境好舒服有大玻璃窗樓底很高，交談小聚都唔錯的地方但食物 麻麻地！（價錢偏高）
大廚都幾好, 味道不差, 海南雞要改進
